alled Windows 10X to market in 2021 like we originally intended, we are leveraging learnings from our journey thus far and accelerating the integration of key foundational 10X technology into other parts of Windows and products at the company. In fact, some of this is already reflected in the core of Windows in Windows Insider preview builds, for example the new app container technology we’re integrating into products like Microsoft Defender Application Guard, an enhanced Voice Typing experience, and a modernized touch keyboard with optimized key sizing, sounds, colors and animations. Our teams continue to invest in areas where the 10X technology will help meet our customer needs as well as evaluate technology experiences both in software and hardware that will be useful to our customers in the future.John Cable, Vice President, Program Management, Windows Servicing and Delivery 翻译（通过 DeepL）：经过长达一年的探索和与客户的交流，我们意识到，Windows 10X 的技术可以在更多的方面发挥作用，并为更多的客户提供服务，这比我们最初想象的要好。我们得出的结论是，10X 技术不应该仅仅局限于一个客户的子集。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Il43No/P9oqJEEAMaCDY0NTU4MjU1IPfykYUGMAc44AFAGnIJNDYwMjUzMDA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"194 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e5a03872f9df51bd510c9f0b01ccd932_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1621501688.8801425","card_id":"Q_266240810","target":{"id":266240810,"title":"为什么刘备那么幸运，结拜了两个都是「万人敌」的兄弟？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/266240810","type":"question","created":1517028776,"answer_count":660,"follower_count":2983,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3676,3679,11066,44749,139513],"comment_count":37,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Il43No/P9oqJEEAMaCDIwOTI4NDEyIKiLsNMFMCU4pxdAG3IJMjY2MjQwODEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"193 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"childre